Package: debconf-translation-manager
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1, python3-requests, python3-bs4, python3-polib
Description: GTK4 tool for managing Debconf template translations
 A GTK4/libadwaita application for managing translations of Debian
 debconf templates. Browse untranslated packages, edit PO files with a
 built-in side-by-side editor, and submit translations via email.
